data.description: Wow!! This home is a truly move in ready home. The property is immaculate and has been completely been remodeled. The home has 3bedroom 3bathrooms, the living room is very spacious with cathedral ceilings, the kitchen has newer appliances and has a newer brick back splash with a nice large pantry. the three bedrooms are a nice size. The down stairs has a living area, full kitchen, full bathroom, with an area for a bed if you choose to use a mother in law suite. The back yard has over a half acre of property and has a new pool and new deck to enjoy your new property. The updates items in this home has so many( new siding, new roof, replacement windows, new shutters, HVAC is less than 1 year old, New pool, New deck extension, New carpet on stairs, Newly painted professionally done, New laminate flooring less than 1 year old. This property is not on the FEMA flood map for flooding and does not require flood insurance.
